Subject: EPP blocking file upload / INC1283751
Description: User is trying to upload file to docusign.upload.com file is getting stuck, browser keeps buffering. No block logs are showing on EPP console, when gave EPP suspension OTP everything works fine.
What_We_Know__c: EPP Client blocked a file upload to docusign.com, but it did not generate any block log
Next_Steps__c: 15.05.2025: A remote session will be scheduled in order to investigate and collect a set of logs
Solution_Comment__c: The issue got fixed by itself. Probably it was a misconfiguration.
